Welcome to mg xix multigame 32 fix

Gameplay:
 This is a multimap with 22 different maps full of fun, minigames and aim maps. You start at the spawn from where a random player gets teleported to the center of the map. First of all you choose a map, then select one of over 16 weapon combos and finally one of over 15 health settings. Afterwards the map will be started. For good measure there's a boss mode which allows only Headshots.

======================================================

What is new ?

-Add new Map (Bhop)

-Fix many Bugs and after update the Ring bug ,D

-Add new Musik

-Gameplay and balancing

-Better Perfomance

-Boss Modus [Only Headshots] now in every Aim Map
